description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Parvati purrs with a rating of 46, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 138, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 5 for East, 8 for South, and 3 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40463-15832-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [138 Votes, Top 15% Score]
